{"tid":1773072,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【今晚開騷】陳小春預備防彈背心演出 台北場館外被塗鴉「支那陳小春滾」","createTime":"2019-12-07T07:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T09:22:28.000Z","uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9759ddfc1393ded323372ab8b7c46cb236011ad1","tid":1773072,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191207/large/1575703480_f12c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191207%2Flarge%2F1575703480_f12c.jpg&h=df3eee5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳小春「滾」（台灣《蘋果新聞網》圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191207/large/1575703480_6550.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191207%2Flarge%2F1575703480_6550.jpg&h=11a30aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現年52歲的陳小春今晚將首次在台灣開演唱會，據了解，陳小春會穿防彈背心。（資料圖片）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191207/large/1575702873_2649.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191207%2Flarge%2F1575702873_2649.jpg&h=42ba2d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳小春演唱會場地外被噴上字句。（台灣《蘋果新聞網》圖片）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191207/large/1575702873_ae60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191207%2Flarge%2F1575702873_ae60.jpg&h=c07c9888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（台灣《蘋果新聞網》圖片）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n現年52歲的陳小春今晚將首次在台灣開演唱會，晚上7點半於林口體育館舉辦《STOP ANGRY》巡迴演唱會，日前他提早來台準備，周三忙着跑電台、節目宣傳，密集彩排練唱，今晚終於要正式登場，令鐵粉相當興奮。據悉演唱會票房賣出8成，不過台灣《蘋果新聞網》接獲讀者爆料，指陳小春下榻的大倉久和飯店外，昨晚已停了5駕以上警車戒備，可說是「官員級維安」。據了解，陳小春會穿防彈背心，身旁安插隨身保鑣，老婆應采兒和兒子Jasper也有專人護送。"},{"pid":"c01b125ce83df1235c75515f484c0d34e9870996","tid":1773072,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"據悉因陳小春有惠州市特聘政協委員的身份，加上可能會有其他中國政協委員來台灣聽演唱會，事前不少民眾在粉絲專頁，表示要去現場抗議，甚至揚言要丟汽油彈，演唱會有高度安全隱憂，警方加派60到70名警力維護現場安全；有附近居民發現場館部分外牆被用白色、黑色噴漆噴上「強姦犯陳小春」、「支那陳小春滾」等不堪入目字眼，更表示：「聽說有團體要來抗議，很可怕。」<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，這次演唱會安檢也全面升級，所有入場人員、歌迷都要檢查隨身包包，查看有無危險物品，開場前也會有工作人員檢查廁所有沒有躲著可疑人物，維安做到最高等級。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191207/60352445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191207%2F60352445&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=1eeb41fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191207%2F60352445&h=cd2fb0e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191207/60352445</a>"},{"pid":"a98e698d9a6f797eb51af19daddb58184639a4c4","tid":1773072,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.jpg&h=ca6df116&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b51c4f508d5543378abd2d4c7a6d1ff5a8ad0203","tid":1773072,"uid":41423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:36:42.000Z","msg":"間諜滾回支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613959a8820d8fa0aa5f20fc2b2217d875b3b4c8","tid":1773072,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/if6q9k4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fif6q9k4.png&h=2b513cf7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"611d96f5421dee6dc36739715a82cf2eeedca312","tid":1773072,"uid":123591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"咁老既 正常人都唔想睇到呢d垃圾阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fca67a9f06e7dc882edd3892aaf00507397106","tid":1773072,"uid":335612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"山雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8544c65bf7bcd0e5a8f45df8b8218f53b3400e51","tid":1773072,"uid":264975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:39:23.000Z","msg":"舔肛春<br />\n賤畜滾回支那<br />\n下賤東西去死吧"},{"pid":"7668e81dfa7d1c6b33f725fe8e3375057bd5ac24","tid":1773072,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"佢唱犯賤同獻世唱到完場？"},{"pid":"cde58f0c810c3e4ab212f7d73de6a41e6400cf02","tid":1773072,"uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7668e81dfa7d1c6b33f725fe8e3375057bd5ac24","tid":1773072,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"佢唱犯賤同獻世唱到完場？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:02:56.000Z","msg":"唱到鬼煉喉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e9b0aaa347c4f859fd81af4fb0a80af83450a0","tid":1773072,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"奇就奇在一隻得共產黨認證的可疑間諜，居然可以公然在敵陣自由出入，還可以搵錢，台灣政府傻夠未？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}